duck: EXI Wireless - Since 1980, eXI Wireless Systems has developed and manufactured Radio Frequency IDentification (RFID) wireless systems.
Efficient XML Interchange - Efficient XML Interchange (EXI) is a proposed data format from the Efficient XML Interchange Working Group of the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C).
Excursion Inlet Seaplane Base - Excursion Inlet Seaplane Base is a public seaplane based located in Excursion Inlet, Alaska, USA.
Exi (subculture) - The Exis (pronounced "Exies") were a youth movement in Hamburg, Germany, in the 1950s.
